            <scopecontent id="aspace_15700f3f5d1b11100b1fbedc060cbf33">
               <head>Scope and Contents</head>
               <p>This collection includes a series of letters, mostly thank you notes from the emperor and empress of Brazil to various Brazilian cardinals. Also found is a miscellaneous copy volume of writings about the Amazon River. The only item from Portugal is a letter by a cosmographer concerning the death of a descendant of Vasco de Gama.</p>
            </scopecontent>
            <accessrestrict id="aspace_a464b5d7e4daefd6415099faaea10339">
               <head>Conditions Governing Access</head>
               <p>Patrons must use FILM HM 254 instead of the originals.</p>
            </accessrestrict>
